1
00:00:36,719 --> 00:00:38,359
Since the beginning of spring this year,

2
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:41,000
raw material prices have continued to rise,

3
00:00:41,759 --> 00:00:43,880
posing severe challenges to our factory's operations.

4
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:44,479
Yingrong.

5
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:46,600
If you hadn't lent a hand just now,

6
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:47,960
I definitely wouldn't have finished that work.

7
00:00:48,479 --> 00:00:49,320
It's nothing.

8
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:50,479
Just a small thing.

9
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:52,159
What do you mean small thing?

10
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:53,159
Thank you.

11
00:00:53,159 --> 00:00:53,840
Getting married tomorrow.

12
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:54,759
Congratulations, Minjiang.

13
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:55,840
My mom arranged it urgently.

14
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:56,600
Congratulations, Minjiang.

15
00:00:57,039 --> 00:00:57,679
Getting married tomorrow.

16
00:00:57,679 --> 00:00:58,359
So sudden?

17
00:00:58,359 --> 00:00:59,320
My mom arranged it urgently.

18
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:00,159
Congrats, congrats.

19
00:01:00,159 --> 00:01:01,119
Isn't this a bit rushed?

20
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:01,880
Be sure to come.

21
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:02,320
Definitely going.

22
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:03,679
Your sister is pregnant.

23
00:01:03,679 --> 00:01:04,640
Is everything okay at home?

24
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,319
Congratulations.

25
00:01:05,319 --> 00:01:06,640
You don't know my mom.

26
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,719
My sister is pregnant.

27
00:01:07,719 --> 00:01:09,280
She does so much for her every day.

28
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,439
It gives me a headache just watching.

29
00:01:10,439 --> 00:01:11,719
Tell her to take care of herself.

30
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,200
Bye-bye.

31
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:12,879
Getting married tomorrow.

32
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:27,319
Aren't you handing out invitations?

33
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:29,040
Not planning to give one to our Wang family?

34
00:01:30,599 --> 00:01:31,760
You really got that right.

35
00:01:31,959 --> 00:01:33,200
For my, Zheng Minjiang's, wedding,

36
00:01:33,519 --> 00:01:34,359
anyone can come,

37
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,760
except your Wang family.

38
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:37,439
Strutting like an old peacock.

39
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:39,719
Even if you gave me one, I wouldn't go.

40
00:01:40,519 --> 00:01:41,040
Be sure to come.

41
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:41,959
Congratulations. For sure, for sure.

42
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:44,120
Yingrong.

43
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:45,719
Yingrong.

44
00:01:46,879 --> 00:01:47,280
Be sure to come.

45
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,040
Director Zhang is looking for you.

46
00:01:48,719 --> 00:01:50,439
He said for you to go to his office.

47
00:01:50,599 --> 00:01:51,439
I'm getting married tomorrow.

48
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:52,239
Be sure to come.

49
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:52,760
Let's go.

50
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:53,480
Thanks.

51
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:56,079
Be sure to come.

52
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:56,439
Congrats, congrats.

53
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:56,920
Little Liu.

54
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,400
Be sure to come.

55
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,040
Sure thing, Master Zheng.

56
00:01:59,239 --> 00:01:59,879
Director Zhang.

57
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:00,599
You wanted to see me?

58
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,560
Bring that document over to me.

59
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,159
Is this it?

60
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,240
What are you doing?

61
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:18,039
Yingrong...

62
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,360
Look...

63
00:02:21,439 --> 00:02:22,759
I've looked after you for so long.

64
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:24,599
Don't you have anything to show for it?

65
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:25,360
Let go!

66
00:02:25,759 --> 00:02:26,319
You're getting married tomorrow.

67
00:02:26,319 --> 00:02:26,879
Congratulations.

68
00:02:27,039 --> 00:02:27,520
I'll definitely be there.

69
00:02:28,919 --> 00:02:29,919
Let me tell you...

70
00:02:29,919 --> 00:02:30,719
Don't think just because you're the Director...

71
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:31,960
...that you can get handsy.

72
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:32,719
Yingrong...

73
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:33,840
Think about it.

74
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,400
There are so many people in the factory.

75
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:36,960
I always give the easy jobs...

76
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,879
...to you.

77
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,759
Don't you understand my intentions?

78
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,360
I'm a factory leader.

79
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,960
If you get with me...

80
00:02:43,199 --> 00:02:44,280
...later in the factory...

81
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,800
...you can have whatever you want.

82
00:02:46,439 --> 00:02:47,680
You mean to say...

83
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:49,080
...I should thank you?

84
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:50,840
Let go!

85
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,000
I'm telling you...

86
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:53,639
If you touch me again...

87
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:54,759
...I'll go tell your wife.

88
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:55,800
Go tell her.

89
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:56,680
Go ahead.

90
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,039
Let go of me!

91
00:02:57,039 --> 00:02:58,199
Let's see if you care about your reputation.

92
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,360
Let me have a kiss.

93
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,319
You dare touch me!

94
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,479
Dare to get fresh with me!

95
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,080
I'll kill you!

96
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:04,800
I'll kill you!

97
00:03:05,879 --> 00:03:06,639
Wang Yingrong!

98
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:07,879
See if I don't have my way with you today!

99
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:08,719
Let go!

100
00:03:12,599 --> 00:03:13,719
Wang Yingrong!

101
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:14,719
Director Zhang.

102
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,159
Get out!

103
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,039
I'm busy!

104
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:20,000
Who let you in?

105
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:21,680
Or maybe...

106
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:22,680
...you two continue?

107
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:23,879
Continue my ass!

108
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:26,000
Listen here, Zhang...

109
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,360
I'm not done with you!

110
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:28,960
Get lost!

111
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:31,120
Scram!

112
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,639
Did Wang Yingrong swallow gunpowder?

113
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,159
That table...

114
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:41,319
move it over here.

115
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,120
Be careful.

116
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:42,919
Put it over there.

117
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,400
Right, right, right. Right here.

118
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,280
Take this away.

119
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,919
You're back, Yingzhu.

120
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:50,759
Auntie.

121
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,439
Okay, okay.

122
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:54,000
Sis, stop looking.

123
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:55,080
Auntie Chen.

124
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:58,840
She's ignoring you.

125
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,639
Why did you bring stuff?

126
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,479
Give it to me.

127
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,520
Xiaochuan.

128
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:04,000
Go check if the wedding car is here.

129
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:04,840
Okay.

130
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,840
Let's go, hurry.

131
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:11,759
Their family would never invite us.

132
00:04:12,199 --> 00:04:14,680
I can't believe you're thinking of giving them a gift.

133
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:17,639
Marriage is a big event.

134
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,759
As neighbors,

135
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,480
we must show proper courtesy.

136
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,480
What a joke.

137
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,279
Do they treat us like neighbors?

138
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,279
When you got married,

139
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:28,279
I didn't see them give a gift.

140
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,079
Sis.

141
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,720
Don't scare me.

142
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:32,800
Sit down properly.

143
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:33,920
It's fine.

144
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,600
The older generation's business...

145
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:37,120
us younger ones...

146
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,199
shouldn't get involved.

147
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:41,000
After all, we grew up together.

148
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:42,959
The bond is still there.

149
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:43,759
Sis.

150
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:46,319
You don't still have feelings for Zheng Minjiang...

151
00:04:49,959 --> 00:04:51,079
It's nothing.

152
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:54,360
We have no bond with the Zheng family.

153
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:58,000
Zheng Minjiang was clearly going to confess before.

154
00:04:59,319 --> 00:05:01,720
Now he's acting like a coward.

155
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,560
That kind of person...

156
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,800
why do you still bother with him?

157
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:06,720
That old hag.

158
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,759
What is she showing off for?

159
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:09,319
The eldest is already thirty.

160
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:10,519
He finally managed to find a wife.

161
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,800
And they have the nerve to hold a banquet.

162
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,680
Mom.

163
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:14,079
Yingzhu, you're here.

164
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:15,480
Mom.

165
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,480
I heard it seems...

166
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,240
Auntie Chen arranged the matchmaking.

167
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:19,519
They haven't dated for many months.

168
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:20,560
And it's already a done deal.

169
00:05:20,759 --> 00:05:22,199
He listens to whatever his mom says.

170
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,480
So useless.

171
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,600
Exactly.

172
00:05:24,759 --> 00:05:25,920
That Chen Xuelin...

173
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:28,319
thinks she's so great just because she's from the city.

174
00:05:28,519 --> 00:05:30,560
Looking down on us farmers all day long.

175
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,480
Bah!

176
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:32,839
Mom.

177
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:34,879
You and Auntie Chen...

178
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,040
just stop fighting.

179
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,079
Weren't you two...

180
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:37,959
getting along very well before?

181
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:39,959
That was because Mom was blind back then.

182
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:41,279
Let's not talk about it.

183
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:41,959
Let's not talk about her.

184
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,199
Feel this fabric.

185
00:05:43,279 --> 00:05:44,399
It's very soft.

186
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:45,920
Using it to make diapers for the baby boy...

187
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,199
will be very comfortable.

188
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,759
The bride will be here soon.

189
00:05:48,759 --> 00:05:49,839
The banquet is starting soon.

190
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:50,560
Mom.

191
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:51,920
Chuan.

192
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,519
The bride and Big Brother haven't arrived yet.

193
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,920
The time is almost up.

194
00:05:54,959 --> 00:05:56,600
Don't miss the auspicious time.

195
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:57,920
The bride is here!

196
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,319
We can set off the firecrackers.

197
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:00,160
They're here, they're here!

198
00:06:00,279 --> 00:06:01,040
Xiaochuan, hurry and go...

199
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:01,639
light the firecrackers.

200
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,240
Okay.

201
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,680
They're here, they're here!

202
00:06:09,399 --> 00:06:10,519
The firecrackers are even louder

203
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:11,639
than the drums at the funeral home.

204
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,040
Sis.

205
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:16,639
What's wrong?

206
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:17,759
Sis.

207
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:21,120
Mom, my stomach hurts.

208
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,319
Good heavens.

209
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,680
It's only been eight months.

210
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:25,759
As the saying goes,

211
00:06:25,759 --> 00:06:26,720
"Seven months alive, eight months not."

212
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,279
What should we do?

213
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,560
Come on, beat the drums!

214
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,759
Over here, over here!

215
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:33,839
Others use cars to pick up the bride.

216
00:06:33,839 --> 00:06:35,160
You got a broken tricycle.

217
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:37,240
Aren't you ashamed?

218
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,040
What happened?

219
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,319
My sister is having a difficult labor!

220
00:06:42,319 --> 00:06:43,879
Let me through, hurry!

221
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:46,639
Sis!

222
00:06:46,639 --> 00:06:47,959
Sis, hang in there.

223
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,600
Uncle, back up quickly!

224
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,279
The wedding car can't back up!

225
00:06:55,279 --> 00:06:56,519
Backing up means bad luck for life.

226
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:57,959
Don't back up, son!

227
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:58,560
Mom!

228
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,600
Zheng Minjiang!

229
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:00,879
Get out of the way!

230
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,600
You back off!

231
00:07:05,439 --> 00:07:06,040
Mom!

232
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:06,839
What are you doing?

233
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:07,920
Why are you backing up?

234
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,199
You shrew!

235
00:07:10,199 --> 00:07:11,160
I'll teach you to cause trouble!

236
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:11,639
Mom!

237
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,800
My sister isn't going to make it!

238
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,639
Mom!

239
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,560
Stop it! A life is at stake!

240
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,120
That's right.

241
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,519
Minjiang is right, a life is at stake.

242
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:19,319
Lao Er, stop it.

243
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:21,240
The eldest is fading fast!

244
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,720
Sis!

245
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:26,560
My sister is dying!

246
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,439
That tricycle...

247
00:07:27,439 --> 00:07:28,519
consider it rented by me.

248
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:30,680
Please help us.

249
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,040
Hurry, give Yingrong a hand!

250
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,639
This is our wedding car!

251
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:35,240
If you ride it away, what about me?

252
00:07:35,839 --> 00:07:37,240
Sis, hang in there.

253
00:07:37,319 --> 00:07:38,720
I'll carry you when we get to the house.

254
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:40,439
Make way!

255
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:42,120
Make way! Make way!

256
00:07:42,319 --> 00:07:43,199
Don't you leave!

257
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:44,160
Zheng Minjiang!

258
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,480
You're helping outsiders bully me!

259
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,040
No, I'm not.

260
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,720
Absolutely not.

261
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,959
It's a big joyful day.

262
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:49,399
I don't want to miss the time.

263
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:50,000
My wedding car...

264
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:50,759
Xiaochuan.

265
00:07:50,759 --> 00:07:51,480
Mom.

266
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,639
Don't miss the auspicious time.

267
00:07:52,639 --> 00:07:52,959
Mom.

268
00:07:52,959 --> 00:07:54,160
The bride is here!

269
00:07:55,439 --> 00:07:57,079
I want to ride in the car!

270
00:07:57,079 --> 00:07:58,439
Welcoming the bride!

271
00:07:58,439 --> 00:07:59,680
Let's go, time for the wedding banquet!

272
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,800
The bride has arrived home!

273
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,120
Doctor

274
00:08:19,279 --> 00:08:20,639
How are my sister and the baby?

275
00:08:20,639 --> 00:08:21,519
Is everything okay?

276
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:22,839
The mother delivered smoothly.

277
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:23,800
It's a girl.

278
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:25,240
A girl.

279
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,160
What did you say?

280
00:08:26,319 --> 00:08:27,639
It's a girl.

281
00:08:29,279 --> 00:08:31,480
Didn't Li the Fortune Teller say it was a boy?

282
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:34,240
Mom, don't be superstitious.

283
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,320
Right now, Sister and the baby

284
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,120
being safe and healthy is what matters most.

285
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,240
The baby is fine.

286
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,399
But the delivery took a toll on the mother.

287
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:41,759
She's hemorrhaging now.

288
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,080
The family needs to be prepared.

289
00:08:46,799 --> 00:08:47,200
Mom.

290
00:08:48,559 --> 00:08:51,080
Our Yingzhu had another girl.

291
00:08:51,399 --> 00:08:54,799
We'll never be able to hold our heads up.

292
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:56,960
My life has been so bitter.

293
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:58,759
I gave birth to three girls.

294
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,559
I was bullied everywhere.

295
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:02,159
When I was sent down to the countryside...

296
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:04,440
I shouldn't have chosen this dump.

297
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:06,559
Not quite a city, not quite a village.

298
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:09,440
And I ran into that family of jinxes.

299
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:11,120
The old one is a vixen.

300
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,840
The young one is a shrew.

301
00:09:13,039 --> 00:09:14,159
The whole family has no virtue.

302
00:09:14,519 --> 00:09:15,039
Mom.

303
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:17,200
Today I saw her family's eldest sister

304
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,000
fainted.

305
00:09:18,279 --> 00:09:19,799
Nothing bad will happen, right?

306
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:22,320
What woman doesn't hurt giving birth?

307
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,120
Their family is acting so precious.

308
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:26,399
Your mom, I gave birth to you three

309
00:09:26,399 --> 00:09:27,120
boys.

310
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,399
And aren't I fine now?

311
00:09:28,519 --> 00:09:30,200
I'm relieved to hear you say that.

312
00:09:30,399 --> 00:09:32,679
Just listen to me from now on.

313
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,679
Mom.

314
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:36,279
I'll definitely listen to you on everything.

315
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:38,480
Xiaochuan is the best behaved.

316
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:40,440
Mom.

317
00:09:41,919 --> 00:09:43,000
Big Brother got married.

318
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:45,039
We received so many cash gifts.

319
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,120
What?

320
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,039
Give me some to spend.

321
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,120
Your big brother's wedding...

322
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,720
don't you know the situation?

323
00:09:56,039 --> 00:09:57,600
That money was all borrowed.

324
00:09:58,559 --> 00:10:00,480
Buying that TV cost several hundred.

325
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,360
Making furniture cost several hundred.

326
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,360
And that radio recorder.

327
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,519
That bicycle.

328
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,320
Just adding up these cash gifts...

329
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,639
I don't know if it's enough to pay it back.

330
00:10:08,799 --> 00:10:09,639
I'm warning you.

331
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:11,559
Don't get any ideas about that money.

332
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,799
And that Wang family.

333
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:15,120
They curse us in everything.

334
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,039
Back then...

335
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:18,120
if it wasn't for their Xu Fugui...

336
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:18,879
finding your dad...

337
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,240
to cover a shift...

338
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,320
and get crushed by a crane...

339
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,799
It was their Xu Fugui.

340
00:10:24,519 --> 00:10:25,559
Your poor mother...

341
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:27,720
raising you three wasn't easy.

342
00:10:28,399 --> 00:10:29,519
It's all that Wang family...

343
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:31,600
that made your mom's life so hard.

344
00:10:37,799 --> 00:10:39,799
The money! Where's the money?

345
00:10:39,799 --> 00:10:40,759
It wasn't me!

346
00:10:40,759 --> 00:10:41,559
Not you?

347
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:43,240
If not you, then who?

348
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:43,960
Running away?

349
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:44,960
If not you, then who?

350
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,759
Mom, it wasn't me.

351
00:10:45,759 --> 00:10:46,639
You never learn to be good.

352
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,559
It wasn't me!

353
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:48,840
If not you, then who?

354
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:49,799
Last night...

355
00:10:49,799 --> 00:10:50,600
I told you...

356
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,799
don't get any ideas.

357
00:10:51,799 --> 00:10:53,159
Hand over the cash gifts.

358
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,080
Mom.

359
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:54,879
How could I...

360
00:10:54,879 --> 00:10:56,559
steal from my own family?

361
00:10:56,559 --> 00:10:57,200
Mom.

362
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,759
Yang Liu took the cash gifts and ran.

363
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:02,960
What?
